  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/a3d496248d6d316ceaed8a08574bfda2.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/a3d496248d6d316ceaed8a08574bfda2.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/a3d496248d6d316ceaed8a08574bfda2.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Sayonara Okaasan is an abstract and bittersweet interactive poem about life, death, and the meaning we find in between.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/32e746d0c9df71772b3f375301d43ca9.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/32e746d0c9df71772b3f375301d43ca9.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/32e746d0c9df71772b3f375301d43ca9.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring original hand-drawn art and music, this short title invites you into a mysterious world where every moment lingers with emotion. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/d42ee1988b244c497d70e17165978f8d.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/d42ee1988b244c497d70e17165978f8d.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/d42ee1988b244c497d70e17165978f8d.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspired by the creator’s personal journey of watching their mother battle cancer,</strong> this solo work weaves themes of love and loss with artistic visuals and an almost stream-of-consciousness narrative. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/57c97db9d77531a78a8a3ceccddee207.webp?t=1733959180\" width=638 height=18 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/ca580f7b8d0ebba5575c39e4495e10a8.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/ca580f7b8d0ebba5575c39e4495e10a8.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/ca580f7b8d0ebba5575c39e4495e10a8.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle-solving elements that guide you through the game by following the words </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn artwork </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original musical compositions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious and dream-like narrative </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonus escape room-style puzzle unlocked by finding hidden items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Available in seven languages </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With its delicate yet somber art, Sayonara Okaasan leads players into a deeply personal and emotional experience that is more than a light game — it is the artist's own reflection of the fragile beauty of life. Accompanied by a soft, eerie ambiance, it might leave you pondering the meaning of your own existence even after it ends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/717e4d4e79ceef210bb162f2dd63e508.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=250 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/a3d496248d6d316ceaed8a08574bfda2.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/a3d496248d6d316ceaed8a08574bfda2.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/a3d496248d6d316ceaed8a08574bfda2.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Sayonara Okaasan is an abstract and bittersweet interactive poem about life, death, and the meaning we find in between.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/32e746d0c9df71772b3f375301d43ca9.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/32e746d0c9df71772b3f375301d43ca9.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/32e746d0c9df71772b3f375301d43ca9.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring original hand-drawn art and music, this short title invites you into a mysterious world where every moment lingers with emotion. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/d42ee1988b244c497d70e17165978f8d.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/d42ee1988b244c497d70e17165978f8d.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/d42ee1988b244c497d70e17165978f8d.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Inspired by the creator’s personal journey of watching their mother battle cancer,</strong> this solo work weaves themes of love and loss with artistic visuals and an almost stream-of-consciousness narrative. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/57c97db9d77531a78a8a3ceccddee207.webp?t=1733959180\" width=638 height=18 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/ca580f7b8d0ebba5575c39e4495e10a8.poster.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/ca580f7b8d0ebba5575c39e4495e10a8.webm?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/ca580f7b8d0ebba5575c39e4495e10a8.mp4?t=1733959180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle-solving elements that guide you through the game by following the words </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand-drawn artwork </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original musical compositions </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious and dream-like narrative </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonus escape room-style puzzle unlocked by finding hidden items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Available in seven languages </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With its delicate yet somber art, Sayonara Okaasan leads players into a deeply personal and emotional experience that is more than a light game — it is the artist's own reflection of the fragile beauty of life. Accompanied by a soft, eerie ambiance, it might leave you pondering the meaning of your own existence even after it ends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263230/extras/717e4d4e79ceef210bb162f2dd63e508.avif?t=1733959180\" width=630 height=250 /></span></p>",
